A few C46 Imperial Tobacco cards for sale (photos/links below).  Prices are firm or happy to trade for C46 needs (5 Murray, 31 Sharpe, 73 Malarkey, 56 Wells, 77 McGinnity, or 62 Jacklitsch).  I accept Check, MO, or Paypal (no fees).  Please add $2 Shipping for a single card or free shipping for multiple card purchases.  

#64 Henline (Baltimore) $SOLD (edge wear)
#34 Collins (Newark) $30 (edge wear, bottom right corner crease)
#78 Hardy (Montreal) $30 (edge wear, crease through name plate)
